translated: Jonsson, William Bunn, department head, Gothenburg, b. 26/9/11 in Gothenburg, son of consul Folke J. and Olga Mimms Davison. Married in 1938 to Brita Dahl. Children: Birgitta b. 1938, Barbara and Beiatrice b. 1943, Bengt Folke b. 1946. Attended Lundsberg School in 1926 and Gothenburg Handicrafts Institute in 1931. Traveled to England in 1934-35 and to the USA in 1935. Employed at Jonsson, Sternhagen & Co. A-B in Gothenburg since 1932, currently serving as chief accountant. Member of the board of directors for Jonsson, Sternhagen & Co. A-B and Bark & Warburgs AB in Gothenburg. Hobbies include sports and bridge, holds various sports medals and badges.
